{"tid":1717284,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[電鍋料理]大鑊飯攻略","createTime":"2019-11-13T14:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T15:05:34.000Z","uid":79471,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a4122176011201bd47b9902805e6f76a41a6c7d2","tid":1717284,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:36:27.000Z","msg":"加幾隻蛋同幾粒蕃茄煮飯<br />\n雞扒皮向下放底 加大量切粒洋蔥 豉油糖"},{"pid":"b32c7a7d6741fe22a976f3aec2356396eb355e0d","tid":1717284,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20332b9cb576db2b603725d32d5d6bbbb6987454","tid":1717284,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:57:59.000Z","msg":"雞扒要放面<br />\n肉汁流落下面好食"},{"pid":"25e32e54857d6fd2fec35feb23343fbb9bf9a418","tid":1717284,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20332b9cb576db2b603725d32d5d6bbbb6987454","tid":1717284,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:57:59.000Z","msg":"雞扒要放面<br />\n肉汁流落下面好食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:58:51.000Z","msg":"洋蔥出水有汁 雞扒放底香口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e963b350d70a5760fc0fb43fda9f3c22980f816a","tid":1717284,"uid":79471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OhhAx28.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOhhAx28.png&h=e1174fdb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37028abca0f37156f0b17e94c7e6265e133e5349","tid":1717284,"uid":79471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:05:34.000Z","msg":"麻油雞肉燉飯 材料<br />\n<br />\n1.薑片：6~7片。<br />\n2.雞肉丁：少許。<br />\n3.白米：1杯。<br />\n4.麻油：1小匙。<br />\n5.醬油：2~3滴。<br />\n6.水：1杯半。<br />\n<br />\nstep1.將薑片舖底，雞肉切小小丁。<br />\nstep2.將白米先行與醬油跟麻油拌均勻，舖至薑片上。<br />\nstep3.倒入1杯半的水。<br />\nstep4.外鍋一杯水，按下，跳起後需再悶5分鐘後即可。"}]}